word1_word2_body2_corebx2_corebay2_word6_word7
word1_word2_body2_coreb3_coreba3_word6_word7
word1_word2_body2_coreb4_coreba4_word6_word7
word1_word2_body2_coreb5_coreba5_word6_word7
